pera.it/tag/roman-sadnik/" rel="tag">Roman Sadnik</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/teatro-massimo-bellini-di-catania/" rel="tag">Teatro Massimo Bellini di Catania</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/vittorio-gnecchi/" rel="tag">Vittorio Gnecchi</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Alessandra Rezza, Anna Maria Chiuri, Antonino Manuli, Carmelo Corrado Caruso, Cassandra, Donato Renzetti, Giovanna Casolla, John Treleaven, Mariana Pentcheva, Opera lirica, Piero Terranova, Roman Sadnik, Teatro Massimo Bellini di Catania, Vittorio Gnecchi"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/e5a356e02fff511c0490461c6f7c99b9" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/foto-mia-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" alt="Riccardo Viagrande" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Riccardo Viagrande"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/riccardo-viagrande/">View all articles by Riccardo Viagrande</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2011/01/le-stampe-amadino-e-le-correzioni-di-monteverdi/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Le stampe Amadino e le “correzioni di Monteverdi”</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2011/01/johann-adolf-hasse-1699-